tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE dance_competition_results (
    result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    dancer_id UUID,
    competition_name VARCHAR(255),
    score FLOAT,
    judge_feedback TEXT,
    final_ranking INT
)

CREATE TABLE dance_competitors (
    competitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    dance_style VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE competition_scores (
    score_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_id INT,
    judge_id INT,
    score DECIMAL(5,2) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (competitor_id) REFERENCES dance_competitors(competitor_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (judge_id) REFERENCES judges(judge_id)
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_id INT,
    judge_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (competitor_id) REFERENCES dance_competitors(competitor_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (judge_id) REFERENCES judges(judge_id)
);
